## Theme 2: Monthly Customer Releases

**Objective:**  
Deliver predictable, high-quality monthly releases to customers with minimal risk and maximum automation.

**Key Results:**
- Achieve **≥1 production customer release per month** for in-scope applications with zero critical post-release incidents.
- Establish end-to-end automated release pipelines (building on daily deployment capability) that support monthly customer-facing releases.
- Implement necessary enablers and migration patterns to uplift legacy platforms (e.g., WebSphere ND → Liberty) to support modern release cadences.
- Achieve **≥90%** automated test coverage for release qualification (unit + integration + regression).
- Reduce average lead time from code complete to customer release by **≥50%**.

